  "subject": "Database connection type reworked",
  "commit_message": "Database connection type reworked\n\nThe Hibernate initialization has been reworked for catalog and request\nDBs as it was not generic enough for those who want to use it as a\nmaven library.\nThe parameter -Dmso.db that must be provided to the JVM startup can now\nbe set to anything but the code will fail to load the DB if the filename\ndo not exist in the WAR resources.\nThere was no way to extend the RequestDatabase class as it was final\n\nChange-Id: Ib9496ed027ebcf58edcd853e263d82d2c00b8641\nSigned-off-by: Determe, Sebastien (sd378r) <sd378r@intl.att.com>\n",
